Signatures.Label: Table(record, ...)
Signatures.Documentation: Creates a table from the specified records, with as many columns as there are unique record fields. For example: Table({key1: val1, key2: val2, ...}, ...)

Parameters.Label: record
Parameters.Documentation: A record that will become a row in the resulting table.
